:"2017-02-05T14:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解班共狗仲係相信香港教育有問題先令到年青人咁反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  根本一過關已經自然討厭中國大陸依個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老屎忽以為年青人唔識上網搵料，信晒佢套濕尻教科書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那人信97係支那幫香港過金融危機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以中共見到洗唔到香港人腦, 就直接派中國人來香港"},{"pid":"58357921068f97217fe8d8fab37f89ba4b3678c0","tid":108536,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:51:30.000Z","msg":"癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b293dba84d9c6114619f452b8c8fea98c295a7f8","tid":108536,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae0ce419016fd9b8411ca97145c0f9dbd47a92f","tid":108536,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84751253cfa4be7deca31e4ee2dee854763a53b","tid":108536,"uid":42550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鄧班細路慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf6be7cbf3acfe7f19257840f3c25e0b3cfc44d","tid":108536,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}